Text:
This must be placed in
/"FSX Folder"/Scenery/World/Texture
Replace the files.
Not for everyone trust me if you experiment with FSX a lot you WILL need this sometime

This file is not pirate material. You should post this where it belongs, regardless of it's efficacy. Likely it is already on some obscure support forum somewhere. I experiment with FSX a TON. When I damage it, I rename my scenery and sim object folders, run the FSX and Acceleration repair, delete the stock scenery and sim object folders, run my scenery mods like GEX and REX and fly. But that's just me.

I know I just thought "Weird..this isnt on TPB.."
You have my Respect aargue keep delivering those great torrents of yours!
